snippet.title: TAGAP 4 - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
TAGAP 4, the latest game in the long-running freeware series The Apocalyptic Game About Penguins, is finally here!

Grab it for free from Itch.io:
👉 https://penguindt.itch.io/tagap4

Or from the TAGAP website:
👉 https://www.tagap.net/down_tagap4.htm
